Class Scheduler.scheduleOrder

java.lang.Object
ygong.APS.Scheduler.scheduleOrder
All Implemented Interfaces:
Callable<Double>
Enclosing class:
Scheduler
private static class Scheduler.scheduleOrder extends Object implements Callable<Double>
The scheduleOrder class is used to schedule all orders in a schedule

For multithreading the precise scheduling process after BAB out the suitable schedules

The class implements Callable to return the makespan of the schedule.
